## ü•â Third: Apify (Enterprise Scraping)

**Website**: [apify.com](https://apify.com/)

**What It Offers**:
- **6,000+ pre-built scrapers** in marketplace
- **Official scrapers** for Reddit, Twitter, Instagram, Facebook
- **Actor-based system** (deploy scraping tasks)
- **Rotating proxies** included
- **JavaScript rendering**

### Available Scrapers

**Reddit Scraper**:
```javascript
import { ApifyClient } from 'apify-client';

const client = new ApifyClient({ token: 'YOUR_API_TOKEN' });

const input = {
  subreddit: "programming",
  searchQuery: "AI coding tools",
  maxPosts: 100,
  sortBy: "hot"
};

const run = await client.actor("trudax/reddit-scraper").call(input);
const { items } = await client.dataset(run.defaultDatasetId).listItems();
```

**Twitter/X Scraper**:
```javascript
const input = {
  searchTerms: ["#AI", "#MachineLearning"],
  maxTweets: 500,
  includeReplies: true,
  startDate: "2026-01-01"
};

const run = await client.actor("apidojo/twitter-scraper").call(input);
```

**Instagram Scraper**:
```javascript
const input = {
  usernames: ["nasa", "spacex"],
  resultsLimit: 100
};

const run = await client.actor("apify/instagram-scraper").call(input);
```

**Pricing**:
```
Free: $5 platform credits
Starter: $49/month ($59 credits)
Business: $499/month ($749 credits)

Scraping costs:
- Reddit: ~$0.25 per 1,000 posts
- Twitter: ~$0.50 per 1,000 tweets
- Instagram: ~$0.30 per 1,000 posts
```

**Key Benefits**:
- ‚úÖ Pre-built, tested scrapers
- ‚úÖ Handles authentication
- ‚úÖ Proxy rotation included
- ‚úÖ Scales to millions of records
- ‚úÖ Legal compliance tools

**Drawbacks**:
- ‚ùå Operates in TOS gray area
- ‚ùå More expensive than SERPGRID
- ‚ùå Requires account management

