## Troubleshooting

### Issue: SERPGRID Rate Limiting

**Symptoms**: "429 Too Many Requests"

**Fix**:
```bash
# Upgrade plan or implement exponential backoff
curl --retry 3 --retry-delay 5 \
  https://api.serpgrid.com/reddit \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_KEY"
```

### Issue: Firecrawl Scraping Failed

**Symptoms**: "Failed to scrape URL"

**Causes**:
- Anti-bot protection (Cloudflare)
- JavaScript-heavy site
- Authentication required

**Fix**:
```json
{
  "firecrawl_options": {
    "wait_for": 5000,
    "screenshot": true,
    "block_ads": true
  }
}
```

### Issue: Reddit Thread Not Found

**Symptoms**: SERPGRID returns empty results

**Cause**: Thread too new (not indexed by Google yet)

**Fix**: Use Jina AI Reader directly on Reddit URL:
```bash
curl https://r.jina.ai/https://reddit.com/r/programming/comments/...
```

